  <title class="- topic/title ">Prepare to Assure Campaign Quality</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Assuring campaign quality requires some
	 initial preparation. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
    <steps id="steps_6221CEA229EE4733ACEB04DB74A54414" class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
      <step id="step_A55B825E165641799AAE49A33268C186" class="- topic/li task/step ">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Review your hosts and move each into
			 the correct host group. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
          <p class="- topic/p ">See 
				<xref href="c_About_Hosts_and_Host_Groups.xml#concept_A22F9D38D79546A98DF578E1B25FA585" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref "><?xm-replace_text About Hosts and Host Groups?></xref>
				for details. 
			 </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_D6293CECF6344885BFC42B1ADC6371B6" class="- topic/li task/step ">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">It is recommended that you 
			 <xref href="t_Validating_an_Mbox.xml#task_4BB8E090CBBF4C56A39BB63BF1ADB964" type="task" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">validate
				mboxes</xref> and 
			 <xref href="c_Validating_Offers.xml#concept_60E81920A21A42ABA6980AF60697B260" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">validate
				offers</xref> relevant to the campaign before validating the campaign. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_12929E4EF5F148F5BFB5F9E5ABE7F3D7" class="- topic/li task/step ">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Set the campaign viewing preferences
			 to permit you to view pending (unapproved) campaign from the Development and
			 Staging host group. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
          <ul id="ul_2734581B8FF24387BE2774EC2E20B1C6" class="- topic/ul ">
            <li id="li_CE94E99936C443DC9CBF42D9F61CD253" class="- topic/li ">
				  If today is 
				  <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">outside</b> the campaign start and
				  end dates, set 
				  <xref href="t_Using_Time_Offset_for_Viewing_Campaigns.xml#task_7050B221739949A598AF79E01816FA3E" type="task" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">time
					 offset</xref> to allow you view the campaign today. 
				</li>
            <li id="li_5F316A101E654647A4AB2DD902E839F3" class="- topic/li ">
				  If today is 
				  <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">within</b> the campaign start and
				  end dates, and the campaign is not yet approved, 
				  <xref href="c_Setting_Campaign_Viewing_Preferences.xml#concept_F07174E860F34A5286AD2FDD0091E11A" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local" class="- topic/xref ">allow
					 unapproved campaigns</xref> to be viewed from the Development and/or Staging
				  host group. 
				</li>
          </ul>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
